Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.63,0:00:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送上残暑慰问
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.29,0:00:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假已经过半了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.28,0:00:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐们是如何度过的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.17,0:00:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…感觉好生硬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.89,0:00:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小猪今天也很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.13,0:00:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早除了平常的饲料五粒之外还喂了黄瓜片…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.99,0:00:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不对  如此详细地报告小猪的事情也没什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学习进展如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不对  约有一位学姐明显不会有进展
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.46,0:00:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯学姐发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.46,0:00:42.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（唯学姐  残暑慰问）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:42.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵  你好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.44,0:00:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假期间你能照顾小猪真是太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在在图书馆学习哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.43,0:00:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被先慰问了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且学习进展顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:00:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然大家都在忙于学习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐也去了芬兰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.93,0:01:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中生活最后的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要留下遗憾而努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.01,0:01:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管了  我也尽情玩去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.54,0:02:59.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慰问品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈让我拿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯学姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从图书馆回来吃了午饭后  又去学习了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  唯学姐也是该干的时候就干的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没在干…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  现在是在休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我把西瓜拿去给她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  就这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  用勺子挖着切成一半的西瓜的中间无籽部分吃是姐姐的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  小梓带西瓜来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就放这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放在她门前了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲调变了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:03:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐好像很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边弹吉他一边吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午饭也是这样的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午饭？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉荞麦面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只吃荞麦面的话会中暑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以做成了天妇罗凉荞麦面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天妇罗
