Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吃——！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食物中毒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.33,0:04:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进  请进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉  不小心睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都来我家了还这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  一时真没认出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎很困呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:05:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天看电视看到很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天从早上开始就一直很困
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.19,0:05:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一放假就会变得懒散啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…把小纯也叫出来一起去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她不是说过爵士研在暑假也要练习的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就带上慰问品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爵士研在盂兰盆节也休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然来了  不如在我们的活动室里吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要去拿钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有老师在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.97,0:05:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师也一起去夏日节了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  我开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们给爵士研带了慰问品来  但没人在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是盂兰盆节啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:06:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师们也有的回老家有的旅游  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这个时期的值班
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了这样工作很有进展很有进展
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  这次是来借我们的活动室钥匙的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不嫌弃的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:14.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（樱桃味）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  姐姐一直都受您照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都让我在活动室里悠闲地度过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个能干的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:37.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（日语口型操，属于最基本的发声练习，开始的5个字渐渐张嘴，最后的2个字渐渐收拢）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯回消息了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有  怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定已经去哪里玩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃子味和话梅味你要哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话梅味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像已经变温了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好安静
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还有别的部员的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  等会儿我们去看电影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看夏天看的恐怖电影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊  澪学姐为了克服胆小的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人来看恐怖电影做特训啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经很可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  澪学姐没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪学姐好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是特训的成果？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但根据这个发展来看  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的场景可能就是恐怖电影定式的非常可怕的一幕…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…  连这么可怕的场景也没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有可能是我认错人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经晕过去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪学姐的手机？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明规定看电影时不能开手机的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧  手机响了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是小纯发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:58.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（乡下果然很无聊  什么也没有～～～～～！！）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:09:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然盂兰盆节不用练习  就住在乡下的外婆家了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很寂寞啊  小纯不在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「回来后大家一起好好玩下吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓想看这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  还是不看恐怖片改看这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看这个的话离下一场放映还有很长时间哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去哪里打发时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  我还没发出残暑慰问呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明信片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在夏日节上花太多了  这个月很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是去打工比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.70,0:09:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等纯回来又要开始玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时薪太低了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:10:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日薪1万5千日元…太可疑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…  那个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇奖助手？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七等奖  纸巾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的还有一等奖芬兰旅游和七等奖纸巾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  里面有红球和金球各一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:35.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是去芬兰了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是我无论如何都想来摇商店街的奖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就提前一天回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轰隆轰隆地转动摇奖机来中到纸巾是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊  请务必赐给学姐纸巾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七等奖  纸巾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇到了～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:11:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  也就是说这里面只剩下芬兰旅游…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓也摇摇看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.13,0:11:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有抽选券
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中大奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:19.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这难道是梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧  学姐  拧一下我的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:26.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.21,0:11:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦不也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能去芬兰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓  恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你…喜你…喜你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TETO  TETO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:43.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（这只狗的名字和「恭喜你」后半部分发音相似）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在去之前就醒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.71,0:11:50.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TETO  再也不会让你离开我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且电影也没看成…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:11:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  准备花了点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道是这句
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么晒成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在外面很容易晒黑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.02,0:12:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  轻音部一起去夏日节了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.75,0:12:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日节？这什么啊！真好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.72,0:12:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯也加入轻音部不就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人…人家又没说羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.92,0:12:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前年和去年都是去海边合宿的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听姐姐说是带音乐室的别墅是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音乐室？别墅？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯也来吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也不遗憾！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯的泳装好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年新买的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:12:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓  换好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:13:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑白…分明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有办法了  只要全身都盖上就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那不是更惹眼了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是在一边晒一晒  你们先去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了  接着～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好凉快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉对不住小梓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去找她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个够高
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓先滑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要滑的话…给你！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律学姐？你怎么在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.76,0:14:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这炒面怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年夏天流行的滑炒面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  就像那样滑下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  等下  那不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:20.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连澪学姐都在？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是吃不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律  我要再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.10,0:14:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.78,0:14:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来  小梓也快滑吧  快滑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  等…我从没听说过炒面什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.39,0:14:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这个就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.83,0:14:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦——
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  爸爸  给我游泳圈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.92,0:15:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们买了炒面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到排队排了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身都晒到位了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很神奇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里吃炒面味道真好啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  确实确实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  夏日节的时候前辈也非常期待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最后因为卖完了而没吃到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在聊夏日节…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上大家住在帐篷里闹着  完全没睡好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律学姐太搞笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羡慕死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:56.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你们那么多合宿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.75,0:15:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:02.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有别墅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带你们去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因…因为部员少  部费显得宽裕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  太羡慕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢说是白去的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音部真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪学姐人又漂亮  贝司弹得又好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:24.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯学姐歌也唱得那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算吗？不过最近吉他水平的确慢慢变好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  不愧是忧的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是记不住专业名词  也看不懂乐谱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差得远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩爽啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  夏天结束前想要再来一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:16:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家从图书馆回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来大家准备放松一下去夏季祭典看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.97,0:17:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸  吸吸…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵身上有游泳池的味道～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要闻我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过确实是去游泳了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那梓喵和我们一起去夏季祭典吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板  再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来学姐不是去芬兰了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我为了这个夏季祭典特意提前回国了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要吃到炒面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:35.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我过去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤玉米要吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃法就要像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是啮齿类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  梓喵也来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:18:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很好吃…但有点焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  焦了的才好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  接下来我们去吃刨冰～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要西瓜的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  没那种味道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要草莓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇治金时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:18.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（冰品的通称，以日式抺茶加砂糖及水煮成绿茶糖浆淋在刨冰上，\N旁边加上以砂糖熬煮的红豆制成色彩分明的甜品）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  小律真雅致
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.62,0:18:19.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要蜜瓜味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要蓝色夏威夷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.27,0:18:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要紫色阿根廷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了没那种味道！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要草莓牛奶好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪不也一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  那边有捞金鱼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿来和小猪养在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这样金鱼搞不好会被吃掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  绝对会被吃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劈里啪啦邦邦邦邦叭叭叭叭…之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.75,0:18:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.08,0:18:59.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但小猪又不大  应该没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:02.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对啊  没问题的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和学姐们在一起果然很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:04.49,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家一起捞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:06.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边在放烟花哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  怎么不早说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:13.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不是很远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:15.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  大家走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵也快来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又在做梦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓  姐姐她们哪儿去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.54,0:20:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.09,0:20:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  纯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也不晚  要不要来轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  小梓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果明年没新成员加入我就去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.47,0:20:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…真不愿那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  但澪学姐她们都走了  也没什么意思了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逗你玩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会又是在做梦吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不是做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…我马上  就要变成一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不行不行  不能这么消极！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要一起努力做好学园祭演出才是！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓  西瓜要吃完了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  等我！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.85,0:21:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我先回来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  发现剩下的午饭～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走运耶～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃咯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  梓喵？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  什么？信？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明信片…没收到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.53,0:22:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「刨冰和天妇罗混起来吃不好  不能一起吃…」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.12,0:22:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.99,0:22:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.12,0:23:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕多了一份…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个要分成五等份很困难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就猜拳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.56,0:23:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…我猜拳很弱  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.04,0:23:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好  那就用这个来决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.84,0:23:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我接受挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.20,0:24:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和…


